==External links== {{Commons Category:dd]][[Category:-inline|Kawabe-Takamori Kofun Cluster}} *[https://www.city.usa.oita.jp/sougo/soshiki/10/hishokoho/3_1/2/r2/dd537.html Usa City home page]{{in lang|ja}}
